	 <title>System.TransactionCount</title> 
	 <para></para> 
	 <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Remarks</bridgehead> 
	 <para>Returns the current level of nested transactions. The transaction
		  count returned includes implicit transactions, but does not include Application
		  Transactions.</para> 
	 <example> 
		  <title>Example</title> 
		  <programlisting>select TableDee add {TransactionCount() Transactions};</programlisting> 
		  <programlisting>Transactions
------------
1</programlisting> 
	 </example> 
